    "Title": "Cull Invasive Creatures",
    "Description": "Highpoint Wilderness Specialists are dedicated to keeping the delicate ecosystems of the empire in balance. A client recently hired us to evaluate the environmental impact of a number of invasive creatures near <EM4>~mission(Location)</EM4>. We\u2019ve determined that to preserve the natural order of the region a conscientious culling of these species is necessary.  \n\nLooking for someone able and willing to help in this effort. Please refer to <EM4>\"The Guide to Stanton Wildlife\"</EM4> in your Journal for further information on the creatures being targeted.     \n\nBest,\n\nWanda Werkheiser\nContract Manager\nHighpoint Wilderness Specialists",
